ygData.messageBody:
That is SO awesome!  I love the creativity of these people.
 
You can actually be *dancers* in the Star Wars game?  Good lord, if we could do that in EQ I'd never get ANYTHING done.  lol.  Especially with the way some of my weapons sparkle...I'd be a one-monk rave!  lol.
 
Birogue of Bristlebane

Wulfric
